videos.description: Jonathan Davis uses his speed to breeze by his defender and draw contact as he finishes at the rim with an and-1 layup to increase the Wisconsin lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wisconsin's Davis blows by defender for and-1 layup) 2020/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wisconsin's Davis blows by defender for and-1 layup

videos.description: The Badgers sink seven 3-pointers in the first half as they take a commanding 53-19 lead over the Golden Lions.

videos.headline: Wisconsin gets hot from deep in 1st half vs. UAPB

videos.description: Wisconsin big man Nate Reuvers follows the missed shot and elevates over three UAPB defenders to flush a one-handed putback dunk with emphasis.
